pain in R knee, affecting patient's safety and independence with ADL completion.
Continued Skill Reason for Skilled Services: Patient has demonstrated steady progress towards goals and continues to express high
motivation to particiapte in therapy services. Patient will continue to benefit from skilled OT services to engage patient
in positioning techniques and transfer training in bathroom of simulated home environment for decreased fall risk,
engage patient in graded balance training for increased safety with object retrieval during light housekeeping tasks
and transfer training without AE, in addition to engagement in compensatory strategies with ADL completion to
increase initiation and overall cleanlienss levels.
