language for auditory stimuli and reduced verbal language skills.
Continued Skill Reason for Skilled Services: Skilled speech therapy is warranted to target executive function for sequential thought to
max independence with ADLs and activities with partner, target short-term memory to max independence with
initiation of meaningful daily life tasks (church, lunch, ect) and following multi-step directions to max independence
with person tasks (ordering off menu, scheduling upcoming simpel meetings with friends, ect). Without skilled speech
therapy, pt is at risk for cont decline, falls, social isolation and anxiety.
