reporting very high RPE with low walking distance, as well as increased risk for falls esp without her AD nearby. The
pt requires skilled PT care to minimize fall and injury risk, improve functional activity tolerance and strength, and
manage pain for improved quality of life, decreased need for assistance, and reduced risk for decline.
