Justification for Continued Skilled Services
Impairments Remaining Impairments: balance deficits, dbody awareness deficits, decreased dynamic balance, decreased
functional capacity and strength impairments.
Continued Skill Reason for Skilled Services: Pt would greatly benefit from continued skilled PT services to continue to progress
strength and balance training, and address decline from baseline. Pt is able to ambulate 200 feet with FWW and
CGA, however, was previously able to ambulate without caregiver assist or supervision. Pt now requiring assist to get
out of bed, but was previously able to complete task without caregiver assist. PT POC to focus on W/C management
training, progressing gait training, and improving balance righting reactions in NBOS conditions all for improved safety
and participation in AL environment.
