? Delayed Recall: 3/5
? Attention/Registration with Digit Span: 1/2
? Clock Drawing (Visuospatial and Executive Functioning): 0/4
? Geometric Figures (Visuospatial and Executive Functioning): ***/2
? Short Story (Memory/Recall): 8/8
With a *** (level) education, a total score of 17/30 falls with in the dementia range. These findings align with patient’s
diagnosis of dementia
