Delayed Certi␀cation and Recerti␀cation
In addition to complying with the content requirements, a delayed certi␀cation and recerti␀cation must include an explanation for the
delay and any medical or other evidence which the Part B provider considers relevant for the purpose of explaining the delay. A delayed
certi␀cation and recerti␀cation may appear in one statement; separate signed statements for each certi␀cation and recerti␀cation would
not be required as they would if timely certi␀cation and/or recerti␀cation had been made.
